DirectorII.class, DirectIIClass.c is ©1996 Jürgen Schober


To use this files:

please make an include:tms340/ directory
and copy the BaseClass.h there.

For SAS/C users (no other supported yet)

copy the BaseClass_pragmas.h into include:pragmas/
copy the BaseClass_protos.h  into include:clib/

that's it.

enjoy
